data.description: Beautiful Ranch style home located minutes from downtown Hope Mils, shopping and restaurants. Home offers an open floor plan vaulted ceilings. Private back yard with a large deck for entertaining. The Hope Mills walking loop is with in walking distance never have to get in your car drive some where to exercise. Walk your children to Rockfish Elementary as it is right across the street.
